    "body": "I wonder if it's worth considering not showing a `Today` label at all, but simply show the date always, just like Discord does.\r\nThis would make this also much less complex, because otherwise we'd have to figure out when to rerender those group labels (which I think would have to be some timer that checks whether the day has changed and then causes a rerender).\r\n\r\n@John-44 strong opinions here?",
